WEBVTT

00:00:00.780 --> 00:00:03.651
Safari ndefu ambayo nimewahi kusafiri,

00:00:04.470 --> 00:00:06.314
Ilikuwa ni mwaka 2002

00:00:06.869 --> 00:00:08.298
Nilikuwa na miaka 19

00:00:09.146 --> 00:00:12.475
Ilikuwa ni mara ya kwanza kupanda ndege

00:00:12.499 --> 00:00:15.304
na mara ya kwanza kutoka nje ya nchi.

00:00:15.328 --> 00:00:16.478
Rwanda,

00:00:17.423 --> 00:00:20.614
Ilibidi niende umbali wa maelfu ya kilometa

00:00:20.638 --> 00:00:21.918
kufwata ndoto zangu.

00:00:22.262 --> 00:00:25.274
Ndoto niliyokuwa nayo tangu utotoni,

00:00:25.889 --> 00:00:29.862
Na hiyo ndoto ilikuwa ni kuwa msanifu majengo.